snippet.title: Total War: WARHAMMER III - Karanak Trailer
snippet.description:
Who let the dogs out? 🐶🐶🐶

Karanak, the three-headed Hound of Vengeance, is coming soon to @totalwarWARHAMMER III as a free Legendary Hero!

'TAMURKHAN - THRONES OF DECAY' AVAILABLE NOW! - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2891700/Total_War_WARHAMMER_III__Tamurkhan__Thrones_of_Decay
'ELSPETH VON DRAKEN- THRONES OF DECAY' AVAILABLE NOW! - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2325832/Total_War_WARHAMMER_III__Elspeth__Thrones_of_Decay
'MALAKAI MAKAISSON- THRONES OF DECAY' AVAILABLE NOW! - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2891710/Total_War_WARHAMMER_III__Malakai__Thrones_of_Decay

Microsoft Store: https://www.microsoft.com/store/productid/9mwc735wd9ck
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1142710/Total_War_WARHAMMER_III/
Epic Games Store: https://www.epicgames.com/store/en-US/p/total-war-warhammer-3
Any questions? Check out the FAQ: https://www.totalwar.com/blog/total-war-warhammer-iii-faq/
